-- Bezeq's Pelephone Unit to Appeal Ruling That It Owes 150 Million Shekels
-- B y   J o n a t h a n   F e r z i g e r
-- 2010-11-01T06:01:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-01/bezeq-s-pelephone-unit-to-appeal-ruling-that-it-owes-150-million-shekels.html
Bezeq Israeli Telecommunication Corp.
said its Pelephone mobile telephone unit will appeal a court
ruling that it owes the state 150 million shekels, according to
a statement filed late yesterday with the Tel Aviv Stock
Exchange.  To contact the reporter on this story:
